Direct Known Subclasses:
XYZDataSeriesItemImpl
public class XYDataSeriesItemImpl
extends Object
implements XYDataSeriesItem, ChildSelectable

A basic implementation of the XYDataSeriesItem interface. It can be used to represent a data item in a DataSeries. This implementation also implements the ChildSelectable interface which allows a SelectionChangedEvent.Handler to be set for it.
